properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 4 at 3:39PM EST until January 6 at 7:00AM EST by NWS Marquette MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 20 to 30 kt with gusts up to 40 kt and waves
7 to 10 feet expected.

* WHERE...Portions of Central and Western Lake Superior.

* WHEN...From 1 PM EST /noon CST/ Sunday to 7 AM EST /6 AM CST/
Monday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 1 PM EST /NOON CST/ SUNDAY TO 7 AM EST /6 AM CST/ MONDAY
